<HEADLINE>
FT  22 OCT 94 / World News in Brief: Clinton to visit Syria
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
US president Bill Clinton will visit Damascus next week for talks with
Syrian president Hafez al-Assad on negotiations between Syria and Israel.
Israel shells guerrillas in Lebanon, Page 3
